rows.label: tev001694_MSG0001
rows.name: Hiya, [ST:playername ]![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0002
rows.name: Aren't VTOL aircraft incredible?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0003
rows.name:
You know Matthew the mechanic, right? He calls our
VTOL transports "V-trancers." As you might expect,
the name hasn't really caught on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0004
rows.name:
When I think of airplanes, I still imagine the old-school
kind with propellers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0005
rows.name: My dad had a single-prop airplane back on Earth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0006
rows.name:
Every time he used to take me up in that thing,
I'd spend the trip praying we didn't die in a crash.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0007
rows.name: Kinda weird to think I'll never ride in it again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev001694_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Alexa why she hasn't brought up...you-know-whats.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_JNK0020
rows.name: Reassure

rows.label: tev001694_SEL0021
rows.name: Remind Alexa that at least she can ride in Skells now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0013
rows.name:
You're very perceptive! But yes, that's correct.
I'm trying not to talk about...you-know-whats today.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0015
rows.name: Yeah, I guess I'll always have my Skeâ€”OH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0016
rows.name: I almost said it! Yiiiikes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0018
rows.name:
Tika said that if she has to listen to one more speech
about...you-know-whats, she's going to have the
maintenance center dissect my brain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0019
rows.name:
And even with that, I STILL can't stop thinking about
running my fingers down the chassis of a...you-know-
what. What if Tika's right? Maybe my brain is broken.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0020
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm trying to prove that I can control my
obsession and there's nothing wrong with me.
But it's pretty hard![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_JNK0030
rows.name: Support[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_SEL0031
rows.name: Praise Alexa for trying to focus on other things.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_JNK0040
rows.name: Undermine[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_SEL0041
rows.name: Try to trick Alexa into saying the word "Skell."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0027
rows.name:
Yeah, exactly! That's why I was trying to talk about
plain-old aircraft.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0028
rows.name:
I mean, transports aren't so dissimilar from...you-know-
whats. They're impressive in their own way, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0029
rows.name:
Much less impressive, obviously, but they make for a
nice change of pace.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0030
rows.name: I mean...kinda.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0031
rows.name:
You know, standing here and talking about this stuff is
really bumming me out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0032
rows.name:
I think I'm gonna go take a little walk down in the
administrative district.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0033
rows.name:
Just to get some fresh air, mind you! Not so I can look
at any...you-know-whats out of the corner of my eye.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0037
rows.name: Huh? You're giving me a pop quiz? Uh, okay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0038
rows.name:
"What do you call the body-shaped models that
science students use to learn about bones?"
This is a strange quiz. Okay. Ummm...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0039
rows.name: Oh, geez...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0040
rows.name: Anatomical dummies, maybe?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0041
rows.name:
...What, that's wrong? Well then, ask me another one,
I guess.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0042
rows.name:
"What do you call a key that can open any lock?"
Huh... Hmm... Key... Lock key... Locking key...
Key lime pie... Keystone cop... Key Largo...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0043
rows.name: Hmmmmmm...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0044
rows.name:
Oh, it's a master key! BOOM! Nailed it!
Score one for Alexa![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0045
rows.name:
Um, why are you gritting your teeth like that?
I'm pretty sure I totally nailed it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0046
rows.name:
Look, I never said I was a scientist OR a locksmith!
Why are you asking me such weird questions, weirdo?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0047
rows.name:
I'm sorry! You look so frustrated right now!
I'm just not that good with word puzzles and junk.
You know? Two trains leave a station and...whatever?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0048
rows.name: All I really know about is Skells.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001694_MSG0049
rows.name: AAAAAAAAARRRRGGGGH! I JUST SAID IT![ST:wait ]
